data.description: Picture yourself owning this beautiful and contemporary pool home in sought after Deltona Lakes neighborhood. With a large three car garage and five bedrooms, this family home is handsome in every respect. From the moment you enter through the stately doorway into the foyer, you see the refinished real wood floors and the wrought iron enhanced staircase leading to the private upstairs suites. Custom tile floors to either side of the foyer greet you with a grand and spacious feel. Walk through to the open kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances overlooking the screened in stone paved pool area perfect for entertaining. Freshly painted and updated. Home warranty offered. Privacy fence and outdoor storage area. Master suite has hardwood floors and a walk-in closet. Master bath has dual sinks and custom tiled floor to ceiling shower. Donât miss this highly desirable floor plan. Conveniently located near I-4, sun rail, shopping, restaurants and more. 30 minutes to Orlando or the beach. Welcome home!
